    "detail": {
        "title": "为何中国大陆除了Ingress之外没有别的适地性游戏？",
        "body": "众所周知，宝可梦GO锁区应该是公司行为。之前有开飞机玩过，但是因为这样失去了侵入式虚拟现实游戏的乐趣所以放弃了。之后不断有类似的local basic类的游戏比如侏罗纪世界，行尸走肉our world（ios），但是中国大陆的地图上是不会出现恐龙和行尸的。<br>\n所以我很想知道：<br>\n这类游戏的锁区（地域歧视？），是公司行为，还是与GFW的开放权限有关？<br>\nIngress就能在地图上刷出portal，别的游戏就啥都没有。<br>\n不过想想，反正我们连人权都没有，还能玩Ingress，真的是太棒了呢。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"aw-upload-img-list\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/uploads/questions/20180803/7ba4a91e9180540c18a35f353b9b8d49.png\" target=\"_blank\" data-fancybox-group=\"thumb\" rel=\"lightbox\"><img src=\"/uploads/questions/20180803/7ba4a91e9180540c18a35f353b9b8d49.png\" class=\"img-thumbnail\" alt=\"Screenshot_2018-08-03-11-15-57-625_com.android_.vending_.png\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/uploads/questions/20180803/f577849b1e849c5a3c062f2bfbba1067.png\" target=\"_blank\" data-fancybox-group=\"thumb\" rel=\"lightbox\"><img src=\"/uploads/questions/20180803/f577849b1e849c5a3c062f2bfbba1067.png\" class=\"img-thumbnail\" alt=\"Screenshot_2018-08-03-11-16-04-181_com.android_.vending_.png\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/uploads/questions/20180803/3cf108cecd83a9fed9d520ea7cb70ca3.png\" target=\"_blank\" data-fancybox-group=\"thumb\" rel=\"lightbox\"><img src=\"/uploads/questions/20180803/3cf108cecd83a9fed9d520ea7cb70ca3.png\" class=\"img-thumbnail\" alt=\"Screenshot_2018-08-03-11-16-12-899_com.android_.vending_.png\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/uploads/questions/20180803/943a7e54345e097c8842f61a7e7205ea.png\" target=\"_blank\" data-fancybox-group=\"thumb\" rel=\"lightbox\"><img src=\"/uploads/questions/20180803/943a7e54345e097c8842f61a7e7205ea.png\" class=\"img-thumbnail\" alt=\"Screenshot_2018-08-03-11-16-35-548_com.android_.vending_.png\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
